{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setPurchaseDelegate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<PWPurchaseDelegate>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)PWPurchaseDelegate"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"delegate"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Object implementing PWPurchaseDelegate protocol, or nil to remove the delegate"}]}],"name":"delegate"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The delegate will receive callbacks for in-app purchase events triggered from","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Pushwoosh rich media content (HTML pages, in-app messages).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This enables:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handling promoted purchases from the App Store"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Processing purchases initiated from rich media","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tracking purchase completions and failures"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Restoring previous purchases"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","text":"Example","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle in-app purchases from rich media:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class PurchaseCoordinator: NSObject, PWPurchaseDelegate {","","    static let shared = PurchaseCoordinator()","","    func setup() {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setPurchaseDelegate(self)","    }","","    \/\/ MARK: - PWPurchaseDelegate","","    func onPW(inAppPurchaseHelperCallPromotedPurchase identifier: String) {","        Logger.info(\"Promoted purchase initiated: \\(identifier)\")","","        \/\/ Verify user is ready to purchase","        guard UserSession.shared.isLoggedIn else {","            \/\/ Save for later and prompt login","            PendingPurchaseManager.shared.save(identifier)","            NavigationCoordinator.shared.showLogin(reason: .purchase)","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Process the purchase","        IAPManager.shared.purchase(productIdentifier: identifier)","    }","","    func onPWInAppPurchaseHelperPaymentComplete(_ identifier: String) {","        Logger.info(\"Purchase completed: \\(identifier)\")","","        \/\/ Update user status","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"last_purchase\": identifier,","            \"last_purchase_date\": Date(),","            \"has_purchased\": true","        ])","","        \/\/ Unlock content","        ContentUnlocker.shared.unlock(identifier)","","        \/\/ Track in analytics","        Analytics.track(\"purchase_completed\", properties: [","            \"product_id\": identifier,","            \"source\": \"rich_media\"","        ])","    }","","    func onPWInAppPurchaseHelperPaymentFailedProductIdentifier(_ identifier: String, error: Error) {","        Logger.error(\"Purchase failed: \\(identifier) - \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","","        Analytics.track(\"purchase_failed\", properties: [","            \"product_id\": identifier,","            \"error\": error.localizedDescription","        ])","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"title":"setPurchaseDelegate:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setPurchaseDelegate:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setPurchaseDelegate:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setPurchaseDelegate:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setpurchasedelegate:"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setPurchaseDelegate:"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the delegate for in-app purchase events from rich media."}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setPurchaseDelegate:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setPurchaseDelegate:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setPurchaseDelegate:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"setPurchaseDelegate:","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setPurchaseDelegate:"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets the delegate for in-app purchase events from rich media.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setpurchasedelegate:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol"}}}